## 9ï¸âƒ£ Minimal Secure Design Pattern (BEST PRACTICE)

```
Workspace access (least privilege)
   â†“
Item permissions
   â†“
Warehouse-level RLS (if needed)
   â†“
Semantic model OLS / RLS
```

---

## ğŸ”Ÿ 30-Second Exam Recall

* RLS = rows
* OLS = columns/tables
* Workspace roles â‰  data security
* Warehouse RLS > semantic model RLS
* Perspectives â‰  security
